ver:decoration-0 visited:decoration-0 flex items-center" tabindex="0"><div class="block md:hidden"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="ArrowLeft"><path d="M9.21088 18.0392L4.62509 13.4535C3.84405 12.6724 3.84404 11.4061 4.62509 10.625L9.21088 6.03925M4.96088 12.0392H19.9609" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-primary"></path></svg></div><div class="text-ds-primary text-ds-body2 ms-ds-2 me-ds-2 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0">Multi-Collateral Derivatives</div></a></li></ol></nav></div></div><main class="bg-main grow pb-12 pt-6"><div class="flex justify-center px-ds-5 lg:px-ds-9"><div class="flex w-full flex-col justify-center max-w-[722px]"></div></div><div class="left-0 z-10 mt-5 w-full max-[1440px]:hidden xl:absolute xl:w-auto px-ds-5 lg:px-ds-9 md:!pr-0" style="height:0px"><div class="sticky top-0 box-border h-max w-full shrink-0 lg:top-36 xl:w-[324px] xl:pointer-events-none"><div class="xl:bg-main bg-white xl:m-0 xl:h-full border-ds-grey-opacity-16 border-b border-solid xl:border-0 h-0 opacity-0 xl:opacity-100 transition-all"><div class="flex"><div class="grow pl-4 xl:pl-0 xl:pt-0 flex items-center py-3 xl:block"></div><div class="-mr-3 flex self-start p-3 transition-transform xl:hidden"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-md h-ds-icon-md" name="ChevronDownSmall"><path d="M7.5 9.98291L11.2045 13.6874C11.6438 14.1268 12.3562 14.1268 12.7955 13.6874L16.5 9.98291" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-neutral"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="absolute inset-x-0 xl:h-0 h-0"></div></div></div><div class="max-w-[722px] mx-auto"><div class="mt-ds-6" data-testid="search-cmdk"><div class="flex flex-col items-center"><div class="rounded-xl bg-ds-white-white p-ds-5 gap-ds-3 flex h-[56px] cursor-pointer items-center sm:h-[68px] w-[calc(100vw-32px)] max-w-full"><div class="content-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="Search"><path d="M20.25 20.25L16.1265 16.1265M16.1265 16.1265C17.4385 14.8145 18.25 13.002 18.25 11C18.25 6.99594 15.0041 3.75 11 3.75C6.99594 3.75 3.75 6.99594 3.75 11C3.75 15.0041 6.99594 18.25 11 18.25C13.002 18.25 14.8145 17.4385 16.1265 16.1265Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-neutral"></path></svg></div><div class="grow"><input class="text-ds-body1 cursor-pointer outline-none" readonly="" placeholder="Type a keyword or topic"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="!mt-0 flex justify-center px-ds-5 lg:px-ds-9 py-11 md:py-ds-7 md:pb-28"><div class="w-full max-w-[1252px]"><div class="pb-24"><article><div class="mb-ds-7 m-auto max-w-[722px]"><header><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-editorial1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0">Linear Multi-Collateral Derivatives Contract Specifications</span></header></div><section><div class="m-auto max-w-[722px]"><div data-article-content="84f012814d35" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Below you can find three sections with detailed information on Kraken&#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts.<br/></div></div><div data-article-content="35204519b722" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Click to expand each section:</div></div><div style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0" data-pt="true"><div class="border-t border-[rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04)]"><div class="relative"><div id="85Bl7Ei4pF_CN0GWYSZ59" class="absolute -top-16 h-16"></div><div class="py-ds-5 flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between hover:text-primary outline-primary focus-visible:mx-[1px] focus-visible:pl-[1px] accordion-header" role="button" tabindex="0" data-testid="accordion-item-header"><h5 class="my-ds-0" data-article-nav="85Bl7Ei4pF_CN0GWYSZ59" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-body1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0">Perpetual Contract Specifications</span></h5><div class="shrink-0 transition-transform" style="width:24px;height:24px;margin-left:16px"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-sm h-ds-icon-sm" name="ChevronDown"><path d="M20 9L13.4142 15.5858C12.6332 16.3668 11.3669 16.3668 10.5858 15.5858L4 9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-dimmed"></path></svg></div></div><div class="max-h-0 border-b border-[rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04)]" data-testid="accordion-item-content"><div class="pb-ds-8 pt-ds-2 hidden"><div style="visibility:hidden;padding-right:40px"><div data-article-content="1oI9vgv5U4pElxNQU7FK2" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have <strong>no expiration date</strong> and an <strong>auto-rolling</strong> feature <strong>every hour</strong>. </div></div><div data-article-content="4Zc1SXSgqsoh21m1vB5Qy" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1">Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. </div></div><div data-article-content="YHg9_FlQiMnA-5SXRCjST" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="text-ds-body1"><strong>Margin Class</strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in <a href="/hc/en-us/articles/360022632452-Multi-Collateral-Futures-Margin-Schedule-Maximum-Leverage" class="cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-ds-brand underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-0 hover:text-hover hover:decoration-1 visited:decoration-0" data-testid="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span>Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage</span></a>.</div></div><div data-article-content="NtZt732DP5UXwg7jAEcHy" style="scroll-margin-top:112px;scroll-padding-top:64px" class="my-8 first:mt-0 last:mb-0 max-w-prose" data-pt="true"><div class="[&amp;_a]:!text-ds-notification-subtitle-primary"><div data-testid="notification-container" aria-labelledby=":R16n776:" aria-describedby=":R16n776H1:" class="relative flex min-w-[300px] items-start overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl bg-ds-notification-primary rounded-ds-notification-md p-ds-4 md:items-center text-ds-notification-primary ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 group gap-ds-notification-non-stacked-md"><div class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 rounded-ds-round flex size-fit p-ds-circle-md bg-ds-circle-primary text-ds-circle-primary" data-testid="leading-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-ds-circle-icon-md ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0" name="InfoCircle"><path d="M11 11H12V16M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-tra